and the youngest son will soon be required to take his stand. But in spite of these trials,

00:25:15.099 --> 00:25:27.910
this family is enduring without wavering. Because their boys they like to run around and play,

00:25:28.630 --> 00:25:33.829
we play soccer together. In the winter, we enjoy skiing or snowboarding.

00:25:34.789 --> 00:25:39.349
From when they were young, we did our best to teach them basic morals from the Bible.

00:25:41.349 --> 00:25:46.869
My parents always reminded me that although they were hardships, I could be proud of being

