imprisoned because Jehovah highly values my stand for integrity. Knowing this gave me great comfort

00:25:54.069 --> 00:26:01.750
and encouragement. I stood in court twice. I was so nervous. I didn't know what to say.

00:26:02.869 --> 00:26:10.069
So I prayed and prayed. And sure enough, just as the scriptures promised, I was able to recall

00:26:10.069 --> 00:26:14.390
all the words I needed to say and gave a bold witness before the judge.

00:26:16.950 --> 00:26:25.509
After the sentencing, my heart ached so much. My son had committed no crime but he had to live

